Interface ProfileMapper

All Known Implementing Classes:
ProfileMapperImpl
public interface ProfileMapper

Profile Mapper

MapStruct mapper for transforming profile projections to domain models. Enriches profiles with localized codelist values and student IDs using CodelistValueResolver for codelist lookups.

Version:
1.0.0
Author:
Jakub Pavlíček

  • Method Details

    • toPersonProfile

      Profile toPersonProfile(ProfileView profile, List<String> studentIds, ProfileLookupData data)
      Maps profile projection to a full profile model with enriched data. Resolves localized gender, marital status, titles, birthplace, and citizenship.
      Parameters:
      profile - the profile projection from a database
      studentIds - the list of associated student IDs
      data - the enriched codelist lookup data
      Returns:
      complete profile with localized codelist values
